nal initiatives&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"text-align: left\"&gt;Advantage: background in defense, homeland security, or C4ISR domains&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"text-align: left\"&gt;Why Join Us&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"text-align: left\"&gt;YouΓÇÖll work at the intersection of technology, AI, and innovation ΓÇö&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"text-align: left\"&gt;helping lead complex systems into the world of intelligent, data-driven products,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"text-align: left\"&gt;while making a real impact on critical national capabilities&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"text-align: left\"&gt;Only relevant applications will be answered*&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"text-align: left\"&gt;#Netanya&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;",
